business complements Borden's Orchard Decorative Products
unit, which supplies decorative printed overlays for
wallcoverings, furniture, floor tiles and other applications.
   Borden, with annual sales of $7.6 billion in 1989,
produces foods, non-food consumer products, packaging and
industrial products.
