</IN>
<LP>
   MORRISTOWN, N.J. -- The management consultant firm United
Research said it has sold a majority interest in itself to
Cap Gemini Sogeti, the Paris-based information technology
service company.
   The transaction is part of a pattern of mergers between
consulting firms and information technology firms, said
industry analysts.
</LP>
